        <updateDate>2005-07-11T19:25:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Telework Tax Incentive Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax credit for telework expenses. Defines &quot;telework&quot; as the use of electronic information and communication technologies to perform work functions, thereby reducing or eliminating the physical commute to and from a traditional worksite. Limits the annual amount of such credit to $500.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
